  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it started they give out flour and different food on tickets.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they put all this flour, all this food, at Hungarian stores.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Jewish stores didn't get any allotments.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were all restricted in doing business, and getting jobs, government jobs or other jobs city jobs, whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then it started-- we had a big snow there all the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That part of Romania was-- we had snow from November to April.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they started taking out the young people, and even older people, cleaning snow, shoveling snow, they just-- the Jews in '42, '43, and '44, beginning of '44, took out all the time to snow cleaning, snow shoveling.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Were you ever taken to clean snow? d I wasn't taken there, because I was younger.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but I was-- I was shoveling a lot of snow there near my house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my father was taken.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and other people were taken.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And younger people were taken.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Other than school, in what way did the new laws in '40 and '42 affect you personally?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Me, personally, actually other than school, it affected-- you know, I saw this anti-Semite especially when they had the [HUNGARIAN] organization, the [HUNGARIAN] party.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the Hungarian Fascist Party, [HUNGARIAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- when we went to Shul, they run after us, try to hit us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
